data.title: Victory lap celebration!
data.meta_description: Eventbrite - Resource Assembly llc (Nicole McGee) presents Victory lap celebration! - Tuesday, July 30, 2024 at Yellowcake Shop, Cleveland, OH. Find event and ticket information.
data.text:
The party is at Yellowcake Shop!

Hi, I'm Nicole. Whether you know me from my past 10 years of running Cleveland's small but mighty Upcycle Parts Shop, or we have yet to meet, I'm inviting you to join me on Tuesday July 30th at Yellowcake! We're celebrating and raising a glass to a chapter closing and a new one beginning and the serendipitous spotlight of being on the Kelly Clarkson Show this July.

Join us:

to celebrate!

to hear about Nicole's next venture!

to peruse the racks of Yellowcake Shop's unique style that Nicole loves!The Party Dress she's wearing in green will be offered at a special price that night!

to meet Valerie, the badass designer and owner of Yellowcake (and participant in Project Runway, Season 8!)

to enjoy great company in the neighborhood that both Nicole and Valerie call home!

and to watch the Kelly Clarkson Show segment with us! It airs on Kelly Clarkson show on Monday July 8th, but we'll rescreen it for fun!

We'll have light bites, light beverage, and high energy.

Bring yourself, a friend, and your joy!

Shopping is encouraged and available all evening.

This is a private party with a drop-in format, but here's what to expect:

5-6 ---Arrive, mingle, peruse, visit, snack

6-6:30 --- Short program consisting of a warm hello from Valerie and Nicole and screening of the Kelly Clarkson Show Segment

6:30-8:45---Make a friend, mingle, peruse, visit, snack
